{
  "stem": "1775.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 122.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We didn't even have a shovel to bury her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Her brother and the other three people and one of the boys from my husband's hometown, [NON-ENGLISH], went with them to [NON-ENGLISH], because that's where they came, originally, from.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And myself, my husband, and another boy from my husband's town of [NON-ENGLISH], and that man-- no relations to me, but his name was Goldstein, also-- he came from [NON-ENGLISH] in Poland.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he just escaped from Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He wrapped himself in clothing, which they were sending on the train to Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And as he realized he's close to Meserich, because Majdanek wasn't so far away from Meserich, so he knew, approximately, where it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So he jumped from the train, and he came back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And the man brought a lot of money with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And thanks to him, and the money that he had, we were able to-- to have things, and to eat, and to-- and the man was, you know, holding us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Because, I don't know if he, without money, if he would do something for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But we came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We went-- me, my husband, and that man-- and they had a boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We went all the way back to Jelnica, another 10, 12 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And that was already after Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "That was already towards the end of October.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we went back to Jelnica.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we came back to the man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we told him, we're going to pay him for food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And we would like to build ourselves a place in the woods-- a bunker-- so we could spend the winter here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said fine, I'll-- I'll let you build one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you got to give me so much, and so much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we gave him the amount that he asked.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
